                        <h3><a href="#">Bibliographic Source(s)</a></h3>
                    <p><table><tr><td>Fitch A, Fox C, Bauerly K, Gross A, Heim C, Judge-Dietz J, Kaufman T, Krych E, Kumar S, Landin D, Larson J, Leslie D, Martens N, Monaghan-Beery N, Newell T, O'Connor P, Spaniol A, Thomas A, Webb B. Prevention and management of obesity for children and adolescents. Bloomington (MN): Institute for Clinical Systems Improvement (ICSI); 2013 Jul. 94 p.  [110 references]</td></tr></table></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Adaptation</a></h3>
