             <p><a class="external-link" target="_blank" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180713040614/https://www.guideline.gov/summaries/summary/47115/Prevention-and-management-of-obesity-for-children-and-adolescents-percentage-of-patients-with-BMI-screening-percentile-greater-than-or-equal-85-whose-BMI-percentile-decreased-within-12-months-of-screening">Prevention and management of obesity for children and adolescents: percentage of patients with BMI screening percentile greater than or equal 85 whose BMI percentile decreased within 12 months of screening.</a></p>
    </div>

        </div>
            <a href="#" class="view-more-button"><span class="icon-expand">&nbsp;</span>View <span class="view-more-text">All</span> (6)</a>


    <hr>

